---
title: Nan's Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Feta & Flaked Almonds
description: Our popular Nan's special seasoning, with paprika, pepper, onion and garlic, instantly adds a rich, traditional flavour to succulent chicken breast. Add creamy feta and roasted veggies for a dish worth enjoying again and again.

*Unfortunately, this week's tomato was in short supply, so we've replaced it with carrot. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nans-chicken-roast-veggie-toss-595300d9.jpg
